Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I heard a noise, so I \Nthought you went out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air is thick and heavy. Danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's wrong, but go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to be up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I was still completely unaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was unaware that Rikka was on \Nthe verge of losing her power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:44.64,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SUN BLOCK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwing! This year I have put up a barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to protect me from the \Nattack of the light beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened last year will be repeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:51.22,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE IX "Resort - Last Resort"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place sure is crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's oozing with rotten commoner scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your petty potato-scrubbing existences.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahoy! Togashi! Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.74,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NAPPING PLACE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this place is pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cafe was named with you \Nin mind, Upperclassman Kumin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.04,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NAPPING PLACE Beach Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.87,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NAPPING PLACE Beach Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya! You're here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more reinforcements \Nthe better. And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce you. This is my aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for looking after Kumin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Togashi and his little sister Kuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these are Rikka and Deko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya and Mori Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H- Hello, I'm Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories, Mori Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We once attempted to summon a \Nsiren at a beach just like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming out all \Nthis way just to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My silly husband put his back \Nout. He is such a scatterbrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we should thank you for \Nletting us stay at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually worried whether \Nwe'll be any help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We have all the things we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, we never made much \Nmoney from this venture...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so don't worry if we don't get customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving it in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is everything I expected your \Naunt to be, Upperclassman Kumin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's all get cracking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. So here's the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shaved ice, juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I think I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, you go over there \Nand do the prep work. I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then Shichimiya, Takanashi, \Nand the freshman will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me! Today, the devil is confined!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a magical girl working \Nfor the happiness of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... It's Kyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your cold juice and shaved ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get our special yakisoba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and all your boat and \Ninner tube rental needs here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:13.54,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,WELCOME
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, I want to have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give you a freebie with your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we not, Lady? \NYou're too sweet to resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been skillful \Nat negotiating like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.18,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.58,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, maybe I will have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a lifesaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:31.06,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really? That's \Ngreat! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deko and the others are also working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:31.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,COLA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your order is served! Dark \Ngunpowder discharge juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.42,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,COLA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your order is served! Dark \Nfried netherworld crustacean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the names of the merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be ready shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone said that her yakisoba was \Ngood when they had it at our house...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I didn't know it was this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to help out a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what exactly are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Niflheimr Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you putting on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark breath of Kraken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squid ink?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing with food and \Nwork like the rest of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, can I have a cappuccino?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I want the fried squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squid again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give octopus \Na try once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Toka, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toka Takanashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not shout out people's names like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You qualify. Want to come to Italy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not determine the \Nfuture of my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you arrive back in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have called.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like too much bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the famous priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she may be an imposter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot rule out the possibility \Nshe is a detached separate entity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, who is that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:30.90,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NAPPING PLACE Beach Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be seven this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S- Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old were you when you had her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think. I must've been 17 or 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y- You are joking, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an Italian joke. Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't laugh at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your training manager's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Cento.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She nuts about Japanese historical dramas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She demanded I bring her along \Non one of my trips to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why she talks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toka! What is that? Is her eye hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It contains incredible hidden power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wicked Lord Shingan is all-powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan, I challenge thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. You are my foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword can drive out evil! \NTry to block it if you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can drive out evil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an assassin from the Mage's \NAssociation sent by the priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Dekomori, am joining the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, the conversation \Nflows so smoothly between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna be death-ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not how you intercept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely that is an easy task with the \Npower of the Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.43,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NAPPING PLACE Beach Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she doesn't know how to answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I, Sophia, will accept \Nthat sword challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to illustrate the power \Nof the magical devil girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Do not steal our thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master's Wicked Lord \NShingan is all-powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not your place to interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Y- Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, show her how it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:29.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NAPPING PLACE Beach Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you ought to step in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's up against a little \Nkid. She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master can catch that blindfolded!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will release my power so \Nyou may know to your peril...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the terror of the Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, Master! Are you actually serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can witness the true power of \Nthe real Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A- All battles must be treated \Nseriously in any situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekomori, stand back and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:09:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be destroyed, real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow up, synapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Zuiss World!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry it's so cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't mind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mjolnir tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Summer! Do you want this \Nhypnoworm I caught on the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wharf roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a hypnoworm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to sleep over \Nthere. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't wearing your eye patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never put it back on when \Nyou took it off this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just rest up tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.93,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,INCOMING TEXT/NTOKA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that couldn't wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't come to Japan very \Noften, so I thought I'd ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I can see, not much has \Nchanged since I left for Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka is still the same, and so are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came prepared for all sorts of scenarios.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I permitted my little sister \Nto live with her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, but something did change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gave me a peck on the cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're satisfied with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani asked me a similar question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I became aware of what Rikka sees...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and what she persues, it made me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The elusive thing that she is pursuing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is probably the same thing I gave up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably the same thing that I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to be around \Nto see what she does next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's what I like about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very easygoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it makes me sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you disappointed? Or are you relieved?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question. I'm disappoint-elieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be destroyed, real. Blow up, synapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banishment, Zuiss World!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My power isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look perplexed, Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess. Is your power fading?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You summoned me the last time because \Nyou couldn't fight then either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was merely a compatibility issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are you losing your power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at times the Wicked Lord \NShingan fades into oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little more drains away each time \Nyou seek out the netherworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at night with the power of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. I was the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you invited me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You admit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my power really is fading!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes forget about \Nthe Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tedious to contain \Nhim! I want to take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off, and trade your power \Nfor a stronger lover's pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be what Hero wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to revive the Dark \NFlame Dragon above all else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to regain the power \Nof the Wicked Lord Shingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am under contract with \NYuta from time immemorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The token.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it in Yuta's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Wicked Lord Shingan. \NLet me see how you truly feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will let you have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in order to revive \Nthe Dark Flame Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and in accordance to the logic \Nof the world and its natural laws...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you need to be prepared to stay \Nthe Wicked Lord Shingan for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No goodbyes are final, no \Ntransitions are permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:15:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes in conformance \Nto the Samsara Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To accomplish this, you may be required...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to obliterate your present \Nemotions towards Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be waiting tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:28.28,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NAPPING PLACE Beach Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for another day's hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:31.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy a bikini and we'll strip off 30%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy a bikini and we'll strip off 30%!\N What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty clever, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rake in the cash today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we making all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were raving about this so \Nmuch yesterday, we sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I've put the \Nword out on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.50,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NAPPING PLACE Beach Cafe\NTAGS: GOURMET, LUNCH, FOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? This is our big opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to become the \Nbest beach cafe on the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lack greed, girl! \NYou're just like Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too easygoing. Too laid back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Summer is pumped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and Kuzuka likes to \Ntake things in stride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In stride?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks very determined to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I really will catch \Nthat deep sea monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and murdalize it once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekolumpy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am here, Dekolumpy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I am your opponent. Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, priestess's assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will avenge my Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all there is to your love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very perky first \Nthing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we have customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! My master may need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, Dekomori is on her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Is that all you \Nfeel for the Wicked Lord Shingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your definition of all-powerful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you under contract with Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, lowly commoners!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a show for your amusement!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mjolnir Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good god! Perfect serenity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you emotionally prepared to force \Nthe Dark Flame Dragon to manifest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am who I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because Yuta was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be destroyed, real!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherubim aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow up, synapses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seraphim, descend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banishment, Zuiss World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Physical Linkage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master's consciousness is flowing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta once told me that \Nour contract is unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will hesitate no longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personal engine activation \Nconfirmed. System released.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pressure rising. Pressure increase, \Nconnection within acceptable levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,System all green.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing core energy supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock bolt partitions one \Nthrough three released.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bio energy injection. Commence EQ connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan reinstall \Ncompletion countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3, 2, 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka Takanashi, entering renewal mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upgrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full armored Wicked Lord Shingan \NSchwartz Crustacea is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caused you all to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became dependent upon the \NDark Flame Master's kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I was on the verge \Nof losing my own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I very nearly lost the precious thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I only found with his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will never let it go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta believed in me, and so \NI will believe in myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I release the New Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super-dimensional Purgatorial Fascination!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wicked Lord Shingan \Nis gracefully restored!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idiocy is spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Satone Shichimiya. \NShe's my childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind of like my chunibyo guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.07,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ITALIAN YAKISOBA VS JAPANESE YAKISOBA\N - YAKISOBA EVENT (URGENT!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really leave them to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I think that they were \Nharboring feelings of rivalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuha may not look it, but \Nshe has inner fortitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Torpedoed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, c'mon! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Restored! The Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New and improved, from \Nall-powerful to ultra-powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that power was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, accept this. This now belongs \Nto you, Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really prepared for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you collect all three tokens and \Nrevive the Dark Flame Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you may have to live out your entire \Nlife as the Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as a lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Yuta told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contract you and I are bound to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is not the so-called \Nlover's pact of the mundanes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the lover's pact of \Nthe Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the eternal Wicked \NLord Shingan, plus lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the ultimate form of the \Ncontract between Yuta and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can! Yuta said we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is certain we can fulfill this pact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you can fulfill this pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will back up your statement, \Nas a magical devil girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt a stabbing pain right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's static electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I will heal it with \Nthe Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I stayed clueless \Nas Rikka regained her power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, still unbeknownst to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...something else had begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I had taken your hand \Ninstead of that token?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could have been me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE CONTINUED
